Augusta Build Loader 1.2 REAMDE

This tool is the build image loader for IBM Augusta project.

== Installation ==

1. Extract the package on your server file system, such as '/opt/augusta-loader'.

2. Execute 'install.py' to install Build Loader to your system.

3. Edit 'augusta-loader.py' to configure your server environment.


